"field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_decision_method%3A145">Voting</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-decision-voting-type field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">If voting...:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_decision_voting_type%3A147">Consensus</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-targeted-audience field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Targeted Audience :&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_targeted_audience%3A152">Elected Public Official</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-audience-comm-method field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Method of Communication with Audience:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_audience_comm_method%3A158">Policy Recommendations</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_audience_comm_method%3A159">Public Hearings/Meetings</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_audience_comm_method%3A161">New Media (i.e. internet, texting, etc)</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-organizers field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Organizers</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-funded-by field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Who paid for the project or initiative?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Government of Brazil</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-funding-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Type of Funding Entity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_funding_entity_kind%3A30">National Government</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-sponsoring-organization field-type-node-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Who was primarily responsible for organizing the initiative?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/organizations/government-brazil">Government of Brazil</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-implementing-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Type of Organizing Entity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_implementing_entity_kind%3A30">National Government</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-initiative-support-other field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Who else supported the initiative? :&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-sponsoring-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Types of Supporting Entities:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_sponsoring_entity_kind%3A30">National Government</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_sponsoring_entity_kind%3A25">Regional Government (e.g. State, Provincial, Territorial)</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_sponsoring_entity_kind%3A19">Local Government (e.g. Village, Town, City)</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_sponsoring_entity_kind%3A20">Community Based Organization</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-resources field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Resources</span></h3>
